OL,3,CMeet the artist who's painting every
OL,4,Cpub on her island
OL,6,FA Guernsey artist has been documenting
OL,7,Fthe island's pubs through illustration.
OL,9,FLouise Le Pelley started her 'Guernsey
OL,10,FPubs' painting series in 2021 and has
OL,11,Falmost painted every pub in the
OL,12,FBailiwick.
OL,14,FLouise explains: "When you are looking
OL,15,Faround any particular area in
OL,16,FGuernsey, what always brings my
OL,17,Fattention is the colourful pubs,
OL,18,Fsignage, and warm welcome you get in
OL,19,Fthese places.
