OL,3,CMeet the artist who's painting every
OL,4,Cpub on her island
OL,6,F"So that is what I seek to capture
OL,7,Fthrough my artwork."
OL,9,FLousie's artwork has been popular
OL,10,Famongst the pub staff.
OL,12,FAssistant manager of The Deer Hound,
OL,13,FMatthew Ireland, says: "I think it's
OL,14,Fvery impressive to see hand-painted
OL,15,Fwork these days. It's nice to see the
OL,16,Ftime going into it.
OL,18,F"A lot of things are done by computer
OL,19,Fwhich takes the personal aspect away."
