OL,3,CMeet the artist who's painting every
OL,4,Cpub on her island
OL,6,FThe Red Lion has become a home for
OL,7,Fmany of Louise's artwork, with pub
OL,8,Flandlord Stephen Hill saying: "Louise,
OL,9,Fdid (our pieces) a couple of years ago.
OL,11,F"They've been pride of place for a
OL,12,Flong time now. We have bought three or
OL,13,Ffour and auctioned them off for a
OL,14,Fcharity a couple of years ago.
OL,16,FAs Louise's quest to paint every pub
OL,17,Fis almost over, she will next take her
OL,18,Fpaintbrush to capture the tavern of
OL,19,FGermany.
